          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>No Free Rides Act </strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to deny the earned income tax credit to any taxpayer whose identifying Social Security number was issued pursuant to a work authorization obtained under any program not specifically established by law that provides aliens deferred action from removal. </p>]]></text>
